              <div class="all hidden" style="display:none" >
                çœ‹æœ±å…‰æ½œã€Šç»™é’å¹´çš„åäºŒå°ä¿¡ã€‹æåˆ°å¸ƒè±å…‹çš„ã€Šçˆ±æƒ…ä¹‹ç§˜ã€‹éå¸¸ä¹‹å¦™ï¼Œå½•äºä¸‹ï¼š<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>åˆ‡è«å‘Šè¯‰ä½ çš„çˆ±æƒ…ï¼Œ<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>ã€€ï¼ˆä¸€ï¼‰ã€€çˆ±æƒ…æ˜¯æ°¸è¿œä¸å¯ä»¥å‘Šè¯‰çš„ï¼Œ<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>ã€€ã€€å› ä¸ºå¥¹åƒå¾®é£ä¸€æ ·ï¼Œ<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>ã€€ã€€ä¸åšå£°ä¸åšæ°”çš„å¹ç€ã€‚<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>ã€€ã€€ï¼ˆäºŒï¼‰æˆ‘æ›¾ç»æŠŠæˆ‘çš„çˆ±æƒ…å‘Šè¯‰è€Œåˆå‘Šè¯‰ï¼Œ<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>ã€€ã€€æˆ‘æŠŠä¸€åˆ‡éƒ½æŠ«è‚æ²¥èƒ†åœ°å‘Šè¯‰çˆ±äººäº†ï¼Œ<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>ã€€ã€€æ‰“ç€å¯’é¢¤ï¼Œè€¸å¤´å‘åœ°å‘Šè¯‰ï¼Œ<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>ã€€ã€€ç„¶è€Œå¥¹ç»ˆäºç¦»æˆ‘å»äº†ï¼<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>ã€€ã€€ï¼ˆä¸‰ï¼‰å¥¹ç¦»æˆ‘å»äº†ï¼Œ<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>ã€€ã€€ä¸å¤šæ—¶ä¸€ä¸ªè¿‡å®¢æ¥äº†ã€‚<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>ã€€ã€€ä¸åšå£°ä¸åšæ°”åœ°ï¼Œåªå¾®å¹ä¸€å£°ï¼Œ<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>ã€€ã€€ä¾¿æŠŠå¥¹å¸¦å»äº†ã€‚<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div> LOVE'S SECRET<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>  Never seek to tell the love,<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>  Love that never told can be;<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>  For the gentle wind doth move<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>  Silently,invisibly.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>  I told my love,I told my love,<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>  I told her all my heart,<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>  Trembling,cold in ghastly fears,<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>  Ah! she did depart!<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>  Soon after she was gone from me,<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>  A travelier came by,<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>  Silently,invisibly;<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>  He took her with a sigh.<div style="padding-bottom:1em;"></div>
